Senior Test Engineer- Koszalin
https://www.globallogic.com/gl_career/senior-test-engineer-18/

Description
We are looking for a Senior Test Engineer to our Team in Koszalin. You will have an opportunity to try your hand 
at different testing challenges in the area of embedded systems and create products which are already in use or 
will be used in the nearest future by thousands of people, in almost all cars on the market. Our customer is one of the 
leading Tier1 Automotive suppliers. The candidate will have to support the existing test automation team in daily work. 
If you are an automotive passionate join us now!

Requirements
QA knowledge and automatization experience
Analytical thinking and good communication skills are a plus
Experience of functional testing in Cluster division
Preferences
Embedded experience - nice to have
Automotive experience/ interest is appreciated

Responsibilities
Test automation in Customer in-house language
Automated tests execution
Manage of tests
Maintenance of test cases
Reporting

